OL,5, Paedophiles are using VR headsets to   
OL,6, view and store child abuse imagery,    
OL,7, crime figures show for the first time. 
OL,9,FThe NSPCC obtained the data after a    
OL,10,FFreedom of Information request to all  
OL,11,F45 forces in the UK about numbers of   
OL,12,Fchild abuse image offences.            
OL,14,FIt found forces had recorded eight     
OL,15,Foffences involving headsets and VR.    
OL,17,FThe charity is warning the growing use 
OL,18,Fof virtual reality headsets to explore 
OL,19,Fthe so-called Metaverse exposes        
OL,20,Fchildren to new risks online.          
